{"tid":545202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不明來歷人士以粗暴行徑阻礙泛民區議員進入會議室 東區區議會會議流會","createTime":"2018-01-30T09:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T13:22:09.000Z","uid":136994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bd4a31c9e5f4f07cb733c74078357442d14ab8","tid":545202,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57771741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57771741&d=dzvI1BAirBGbvweE%2Fv9WyUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3016a7cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57771741&h=7f5d31bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57771741</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517298553_b27e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517298553_b27e.jpg&h=e986a1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517298779_d903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517298779_d903.jpg&h=7d4c14dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東區區會今日舉行大會，10名民主派區議員擬提出加入臨時議程，要求討論香港眾志周庭被DQ的問題，因為DQ周的港島區選舉主任鄧如欣，會以東區民政事務專員身份出席今日下午的會議。周庭亦打算到場旁聽稱，並希望當面質問鄧，有何法理依據DQ她、是否有其他權力機關與她作出DQ的決定等。<br />\n<br />\n不過，下午開會時，在場多名不明來歷人士拒絕泛民區議員入場開會，引發衝突，在場的泛民區議員即高呼：「我哋區議員嚟㗎！」質疑對方做法違規，期間東區區會主席黃建彬在會議室內未有理會，反而自由黨的邵家輝看不過眼，不斷來回門口與會議室之間，要求區會主席和職員開門，但他們無動於衷。雙方擾攘近十分鐘後，區會主席才出來表示可讓議員進入。但入場時民主派區員又再遭阻攔，而周庭亦被阻撓入場。結果法定時間15分鐘過後，主席即宣佈會議流會，民主派未能提出臨時議程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班泛民議員識做嘅就發大件事嚟攻擊建制派啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最起碼都要嚴厲譴責啲粗暴阻礙會議進行嘅行為呀嘛<br />\n咁都唔識嘅就抵你地畀建制派㩒住嚟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"f85e23c78b483738608f4e9eee5f3079968687cd","tid":545202,"uid":60959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係唔識打，係唔使打<br />\n中国人不打中国人 🇨🇳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"f1cad339e56453fa4f962814d69124aa50be2d1d","tid":545202,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"五毛狗會話: 泛民乜鳩都做唔到，投奶共派好過啦。"},{"pid":"e0fc1a05f2438875498b1d3cc8fd1165dde536ad","tid":545202,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517298779_d903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517298779_d903.jpg&h=7d4c14dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩條基佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ff9ff79457f0a9932b303cfa6067dec04c45f","tid":545202,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cad339e56453fa4f962814d69124aa50be2d1d","tid":545202,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"五毛狗會話: 泛民乜鳩都做唔到，投奶共派好過啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"咁泛民依家嚴厲譴責左未呀柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老尾真係弱智仔黎"},{"pid":"5ae4b36b36ff518b82c63e688b22d7a23c3a0ba4","tid":545202,"uid":10292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f85e23c78b483738608f4e9eee5f3079968687cd","tid":545202,"uid":60959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color